relation: A sketch of a Farm Zombie and some other Halloweeny sketches.

Flint with an orangey background; a continuation of this . I thought that it needed a background, and this shade of orange, I thought, worked well. Looking at it afterward made me think of "Van Gogh", though, which I suppose isn't so terrible.
Was originally made for Cap'n Muffin's and chuggaaconroy's EarthBound: Memoirs fangame.
